snippet.title: Power Rangers MEGAFORCE 3DS Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Go, Go Megaforce! 

Rangers Megaforce is now available for Nintendo 3DS.

For as long as evil has threatened the Earth, there have been teams of Power Rangers sworn to protect it. The Power Rangers Megaforce are the planet's newest defenders. For the first time, experience the next chapter in the Power Rangers legacy in 3-D! Plus power up your rangers with the all-new card scanning feature which allows you to power up your Rangers!

*Exclusive official Power Rangers trading card included while supplies last.
 
BUY NOW - http://bit.ly/15rBE5R
